    "translation":{"eng":"All glories, all glories to Śrī Nityānanda Prabhu, the son of Rohiṇī. To deliver the fallen souls, He extends His two arms."}},{
    "lines":[
      [{"w":"গদ","h":" ","s":{"eng":"choked"},"o":{}},{"w":"গদ","h":" ","s":{"eng":"⬅1"},"o":{}},{"w":"মধুর","h":" ","s":{"eng":"sweet"},"o":{}},{"w":"মধুর","h":" ","s":{"eng":"sweet"},"o":{}},{"w":"আধো","h":" ","s":{"eng":"mumbling, babbling"},"o":{}},{"w":"বোল","h":" ।","s":{"eng":"words"},"o":{}}],
