    "translation":{"eng":"Overflowing with prema, His eyes always roll about restlessly, looking like bumblebees hovering over a golden lotus."}},{
    "lines":[
      [{"w":"দয়ার","h":" ","s":{"eng":"Lord of mercy"},"o":{}},{"w":"ঠাকুর","h":" ","s":{"eng":"⬅1"},"o":{}},{"w":"নিতাই","h":" ","s":{"eng":"Śrī Nitāi"},"o":{}},{"w":"পর","h":"-","s":{"eng":"others"},"o":{}},{"w":"দুঃখ","h":" ","s":{"eng":"suffering"},"o":{}},{"w":"জানে","h":" ।","s":{"eng":"He knows"},"o":{}}],
      [{"w":"হরিনামের","h":" ","s":{"eng":"of the names of Hari"},"o":{}},{"w":"মালা","h":" ","s":{"eng":"garland"},"o":{}},{"w":"গাঁথি’","h":" ","s":{"eng":"having strung"},"o":{}},{"w":"দিল","h":" ","s":{"eng":"He gave"},"o":{}},{"w":"জগজনে","h":" ॥৪॥","s":{"eng":"the world + to the people"},"o":{}}]],
    "translation":{"eng":"The merciful Lord, Śrī Nitāi, knows the sufferings of others. He has strung together a garland of the holy names, which He has bestowed upon the people of this world."}},{
    "lines":[
      [{"w":"পাপী","h":"-","s":{"eng":"sinners"},"o":{}},{"w":"পাষণ্ডী","h":" ","s":{"eng":"atheists"},"o":{}},{"w":"যত","h":" ","s":{"eng":"whatever"},"o":{}},{"w":"করিল","h":" ","s":{"eng":"He subdued"},"o":{}},{"w":"দলন","h":" ।","s":{"eng":"⬅1"},"o":{}}],
